comments: Holiday (MIL) is moving alongside Beal's (WAS) path and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the drive.
Kispert (WAS) establishes himself in Holiday's (MIL) path and does not deliver illegal contact as the pick is set.
Avdija (WAS) steps out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.
Avdija (WAS) steps toward Antetokounmpo (MIL) and marginal body contact occurs as they come together during the pass.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) steps out of bounds while in possession of the ball.
Avdija (WAS) extends his arm outside the frame of his body and delivers illegal contact that affects Holiday's (MIL) ability to defend over the pick.
Beal (WAS) slightly extends his arms into Antetokounmpo's (MIL) body during the shot attempt by Holiday (MIL) and the contact is marginal.
Beal (WAS) establishes his right foot as his pivot and maintains it as he starts his dribble.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is moving alongside Beal's (WAS) path and marginal body contact occurs as Beal releases away at the end of the drive.
Beal (WAS) steps out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.
Holiday (MIL) briefly places his hands on Porzingis (WAS) but the contact is marginal and does not dislodge him from his position during the errant pass.
Avdija (WAS) wraps Antetokounmpo (MIL) and the contact affects his SQBR during the drive.
Avdija (WAS) wraps his arm around Holiday's (MIL) side and the contact affects his FOM as he attempts to get to the pass.
Allen (MIL) reaches in and incidental hand on ball contact occurs with Avdija (WAS) during his driving shot attempt.
Porzingis (WAS) attempts a take foul on Carter (MIL) and marginal contact occurs as the ball becomes loose.
Wright (WAS) attempts to commit a take foul on Holiday (MIL) as they come together during the drive and marginal contact occurs.
Beal (WAS) reaches in and initiates contact with Holiday's (MIL) arm during the drive that affects his SQBR.
